338
00:15:51,717 --> 00:15:53,844
Have you tried leaving it blank?

339
00:15:56,388 --> 00:15:59,551
Tough to get into the head of someone
who actually trusts people, huh?

340
00:16:00,526 --> 00:16:04,257
Found both computers in an
office on a desk they share.

341
00:16:04,363 --> 00:16:06,695
No sign of macular
degeneration or optic neuritis.

342
00:16:06,765 --> 00:16:08,027
Her eyes are completely normal.

343
