You don't need her. I know.

362
00:16:59,385 --> 00:17:01,182
Then this serves no medical purpose.

363
00:17:01,253 --> 00:17:04,120
You have a genetic defect,
choose to ignore it.

364
00:17:04,223 --> 00:17:05,884
This woman has a genetic defect,

365
00:17:05,991 --> 00:17:08,186
chooses to butcher herself to be safe.

366
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:11,923
Yet, what you claim to be
fascinated by is her honesty.

367
00:17:12,031 --> 00:17:13,225
Interesting.

368
00:17:13,298 --> 00:17:15,232
You claim to want the truth.

369
00:17:15,300 --> 00:17:18,360
And then you screw with people
who actually live by it. Pathetic.

370
00:17:18,437 --> 00:17:21,235
Hey, I gave you credit for interesting.

371
00:17:22,374 --> 00:17:25,707
