00:20:10,809 --> 00:20:12,470
How do you know no?

427
00:20:12,578 --> 00:20:14,443
I know you didn't get House.

428
00:20:15,781 --> 00:20:17,646
I know he didn't get House.

429
00:20:18,584 --> 00:20:21,212
You gave them all your name? Mmm-hmm.

430
00:20:21,286 --> 00:20:25,450
I figured I could sow some dissension
and get a few ties and sweaters.

431
00:20:25,557 --> 00:20:27,184
What happens when they find out?

432
00:20:27,259 --> 00:20:28,726
It's Secret Santa.

