496
00:23:54,366 --> 00:23:55,924
I've been looking for this all morning.

497
00:23:56,001 --> 00:23:57,764
Did you look in the box on my desk?

498
00:23:57,836 --> 00:24:00,202
Oh, by the way, your mom
called. Your dad's dead.

499
00:24:01,473 --> 00:24:03,464
You left the present
sitting on your desk?

500
00:24:03,542 --> 00:24:06,204
