520
00:25:02,734 --> 00:25:04,258
What's wrong?

521
00:25:05,604 --> 00:25:07,595
Maggie tested negative for sarcoidosis.

522
00:25:07,706 --> 00:25:10,197
But she's bleeding into her eyes, now.

523
00:25:10,275 --> 00:25:11,572
Have her platelets dropped?

524
00:25:11,643 --> 00:25:13,440
Plummeted. New labs
show they're under 40.

525
00:25:13,512 --> 00:25:15,503
She'll bleed out of every orifice
if we don't find the cause.

526
00:25:15,580 --> 00:25:17,741
Could be splenic
sequestration, tuberculosis.

527
00:25:17,816 --> 00:25:19,215
Gaucher disease, TTP.

528
00:25:19,284 --> 00:25:21,184
Hemolytic-uremic
syndrome, sepsis, lupus...

529
00:25:21,253 --> 00:25:23,778
