than one Secret Santa.

537
00:25:51,082 --> 00:25:53,983
Or somebody else wants to make me happy.

538
00:25:57,155 --> 00:25:58,816
Merry Christmas.

539
00:26:16,474 --> 00:26:19,466
On the one hand, you should be in bed.

540
00:26:19,578 --> 00:26:23,173
On the other hand, I told you
to rest. So, I see your dilemma.

541
00:26:23,281 --> 00:26:25,943
Hey, I don't think
resting is the problem.

542
00:26:26,017 --> 00:26:28,349
Can strep cause this?

543
00:26:29,487 --> 00:26:30,647
Clap on.

544
00:26:30,722 --> 00:26:32,622
Trust me, first place I went.

545
00:26:33,625 --> 00:26:36,856
No rash on my labia. Do
you need to take a look?

546
00:26:37,862 --> 00:26:40,854
I'm saving my money
for a Red Rider BB gun.

547
00:26:43,668 --> 00:26:45,295
Darker shade of lipstick?

548
00:26:45,370 --> 00:26:46,928
I'm not wearing any.

549
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:54,335
You tell your mother what you do?

550
00:26:54,446 --> 00:26:56,107
It doesn't matter. I'm curious.

551
00:26:57,015 --> 00:26:59,813
I don't need to break her heart
just so I can feel righteous.

552
00:27:07,058 --> 00:27:08,525
Do you do a donkey show?

553
00:27:09,661 --> 00:27:11,993
I'm not curious. It matters.

554
00:27:14,733 --> 00:27:17,065
It's a donkey or a mule.

555
00:27:18,970 --> 00:27:20,835
I can never remember.

556
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:24,470
Wow. That is a creepy smile.

557
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:27,371
I bet the donkey's is even creepier.

558
00:27:28,146 --> 00:27:29,807
Do I have to explain... Nope.

559
00:27:30,515 --> 00:27:31,641
That's my job.

560
00:27:31,716 --> 00:27:33,149
Contagious ecthyma.

561
00:27:33,218 --> 00:27:37,552
Any contact can cause rashes,
flu symptoms, sore throat.

562
00:27:37,656 --> 00:27:38,782
Has there been

563
00:27:39,124 --> 00:27:40,113
contact?

564
00:27:42,861 --> 00:27:45,694
Okay. Antibiotic cream for you

565
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:48,264
