567
00:27:53,838 --> 00:27:57,137
You should come and see the
show. I think you'd like it.

568
00:27:57,909 --> 00:27:59,900
Sorry. I hate Westerns.

569
00:28:13,725 --> 00:28:14,987
So, they really never lie?

570
00:28:15,060 --> 00:28:16,391
Doesn't seem like it.

571
00:28:16,461 --> 00:28:17,553
Admirable.

572
00:28:17,629 --> 00:28:18,653
You tell Cameron everything?

573
00:28:18,730 --> 00:28:20,095
No.

574
00:28:20,799 --> 00:28:22,289
You think she keeps secrets?

575
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:26,131
If I knew, they wouldn't
be secrets. I hope she does.

576
00:28:26,237 --> 00:28:29,764
People have a right to a little
privacy, even from the people they love.

577
00:28:34,713 --> 00:28:36,044
Did you buy House a present?

578
00:28:36,581 --> 00:28:38,344
Why would I? To screw with me.

579
00:28:38,416 --> 00:28:39,747
Then, I'm gonna say yes.

580
00:28:40,585 --> 00:28:42,780
No, wait. Stop. Stop. What's that smell?

581
