We ran a full body bone scan to find
the cause of hardening in the hip.

584
00:28:59,771 --> 00:29:00,931
No hot spots anywhere.

585
00:29:01,005 --> 00:29:02,495
Tracer could have been inactive.

586
00:29:02,607 --> 00:29:04,165
So, I screwed up the test?

587
00:29:04,275 --> 00:29:05,867
There are so many ways
that could have happened.

588
