to get home before Santa.

743
00:38:27,004 --> 00:38:28,494
Scrooge.

744
00:38:28,572 --> 00:38:29,800
Give the patient risperidone.

745
00:38:30,574 --> 00:38:33,372
That's an anti-psychotic.
She's dying. She's not crazy.

746
00:38:33,444 --> 00:38:36,777
I am gonna perform a Christmas miracle.

747
00:38:36,881 --> 00:38:41,648
<i>Oh, tidings of comfort
and joy Comfort and joy</i>

748
00:38:42,853 --> 00:38:45,879
You said all the other causes
of osteopetrosis are fatal.

749
00:38:45,956 --> 00:38:49,687
Except for the one we discounted
early because it was impossible.

750
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:52,729
When a fetus forms, it's
just a mass of cells.

751
00:38:53,731 --> 00:38:57,064
